Jones and another death-row inmate, Edward Schad, filed a lawsuit against the state to get the Arizona Department of Corrections to reveal the source of the barbiturate pentobarbital, which would be used in both men's executions. The two men appeared side by side on closed-circuit TV during the federal court hearings earlier this month.
